        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3704262304" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17007347756497903517">In contrast to most books that relates to addiction in general and opioid addiction in particular, this exceptional novel by Bulgakov portrays a young doctors rapid descent into morphine abuse.<br/><br/>Bulgakov writing is simplistic and precise, but never the less powerful. The only thing I could’ve asked for is for the novel to be a tad bit longer!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


