<div id="review_1439115729" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1439115729" />
    <a title="Emily" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14016020-emily"><img alt="Emily" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1351388399p2/14016020.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1439115729?book_show_action=true">Nov 10, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Emily" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Emily" href="/user/show/14016020-emily">Emily</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780811221689" href="/book/show/17574852-morphine">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14016020-emily?shelf=world">world</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14016020-emily?shelf=pain">pain</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14016020-emily?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14016020-emily?shelf=translation">translation</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14016020-emily?shelf=novella">novella</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1439115729" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12291410271397268905">Bulgakov&apos;s great masterwork is &quot;The Master and Margarita.&quot; &quot;Morphine&quot; has none of the fireworks and flashiness that is found in &quot;The Master and Margarita,&quot; but it is a jewel. Bulgakov was a doctor himself and &quot;Morphine&quot; was written with great care in discovery of the suffering &quot;other.&quot; Some may call it a short-story, it&apos;s recently been published as a novella, either way only a few hours reading but well worth it. </span>
  <span id="freeText12291410271397268905" style="display:none">Bulgakov's great masterwork is "The Master and Margarita." "Morphine" has none of the fireworks and flashiness that is found in "The Master and Margarita," but it is a jewel. Bulgakov was a doctor himself and "Morphine" was written with great care in discovery of the suffering "other." Some may call it a short-story, it's recently been published as a novella, either way only a few hours reading but well worth it. </span>
  <a data-text-id="12291410271397268905" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
