<li class='cover' id='bookCover_36551766'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/36551766-ranocchio-salva-tokyo"><img alt="Ranocchio salva Tokyo" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1510954215l/36551766._SX98_.jpg" />
